name: NEFilterBrowserFlow
desc: A flow of network data, originating from a WebKit-based browser, that the filter examines.

items.name: var parentURL: URL?
items.desc: An NSURL object containing the URL of the web page that caused this flow to be created.

items.name: var request: URLRequest?
items.desc: An NSURLRequest object containing the HTTP request of the flow.

items.name: var response: URLResponse?
items.desc: An URLResponse object containing the HTTP response of the flow.
